{"tid":697302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傻的「媽」？！為了20萬，澳門一女子性侵兒子拍埋片！！","createTime":"2018-06-11T01:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T08:01:15.000Z","uid":47132,"like":56,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"154e5f39c1349e76aa3ae2f59454c0a2c54c52db","tid":697302,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www-twgreatdaily-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/62/6265955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-twgreatdaily-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F62%2F6265955.jpg&h=f41fcb34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1名27歲澳門女子涉嫌性侵犯3歲兒子，並拍攝短片交陌生男子獲取報酬，被司警拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n司警接到學校舉報，指有1名女子性侵兒童的短片在手機聊天室家長群組內流傳，隨即拘捕嫌疑人。<br />\n<br />\n她供稱是透過網絡平台認識1名男子，<br />\n<br />\n男子聲稱她若與兒子發生性行為，<br />\n<br />\n並將過程拍攝短片，<br />\n<br />\n連同手機聊天軟體密碼交給對方，<br />\n<br />\n則可獲得20萬報酬，<br />\n<br />\n嫌疑人隨即於當晚作案。<br />\n<br />\n司警表示，嫌疑人與丈夫分居，<br />\n<br />\n兒子與她的丈夫同住，<br />\n<br />\n懷疑她與兒子外出在友人家中時趁機作案。<br />\n<br />\n司警稱，嫌疑人最終沒有取得任何金錢利益，<br />\n<br />\n嫌疑人也是片段流傳的聊天室群組成員。<br />\n<br />\n司警仍在追查誘使嫌疑人犯案的人的下落。"},{"pid":"53319d3184b75e53f446399d16b4819ae12cafdd","tid":697302,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b1cee43610695e85034fe01e2291d7bbd6b98f","tid":697302,"uid":51701,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"澳狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8473ff34aabf9fb027a008259f98efce3938a92e","tid":697302,"uid":37005,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:24:37.000Z","msg":"智障狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7511d95f3e2c5a1044a73f15775c34f2235aac","tid":697302,"uid":838,"like":1